# Implementation Plan - Phase 5: Interactive Coding Labs

This plan covers the development of a state-of-the-art coding environment within the LMS, providing students with an immersive development experience.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Code Execution**: For multi-language support (Python, Java, etc.), we will use the **Piston API** (a free, industrial-grade execution engine). JavaScript will be executed locally in a secure sandbox for instant feedback.
> **Dependency Installation**: This phase requires installing `@monaco-editor/react`. Please confirm you are okay with this additional package.

